member.name: T:HL.Common.ValueObjects.CountryType
member.summary: Encapsulates a country value

remarks.para: This class does an imperfect job at mapping back from ISO country code to HMS / Herbalife code. The reason is that there are potentially multiple HMS codes that map to a single ISO code, so reversing is ambigous. See xxhl.xhl_dm_country_mapping.
The countries subject to ambiguity are: China CN - (CH, CN), UnitedKingdom GB - (UK, JE, GK, IM), Greece GR - (HE, GR), Russia RU - (RS, RU)
